item.title: UA Baseball Factory
item.dc:creator: dustin
item.content:encoded:
UA Baseball Factory

Baseball Factory and Under Armour have joined forces to discover and develop the best high school baseball players in the country. It all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour where players are evaluated by our professional instructors. Top players are then invited to attend National Team, National Training, and All-America events. There they receive high-level instruction, compete against other top prospects, and play in front of college coaches.
